<sect1 id="history-menu">
<title>The <guimenu>History</guimenu> Menu</title>

<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">
&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap>
</keycombo></shortcut>
<guimenu>History</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
<guiicon>
<inlinemediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="undo.png" format="PNG"/>
</imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Undo Icon</phrase></textobject>
</inlinemediaobject>
</guiicon>.
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Reverses the last action you performed. Not all actions can
be reversed. If you are unable to Undo the last action, the
<quote>Undo</quote> option will be replaced with <quote>No Undo
Possible</quote>.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">
&Ctrl;<keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Z</keycap>
</keycombo></shortcut>
<guimenu>History</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
<guiicon>
<inlinemediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="redo.png" format="PNG"/>
</imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Redo Icon</phrase></textobject>
</inlinemediaobject>
</guiicon>.
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Reverses the last Undo performed. If the Redo option is
unavailable, the <quote>Redo</quote> options will be replaced with
<quote>No Redo Possible</quote>.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="settings-menu">
<title>The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> Menu</title>

<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Tool Settings</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>This displays a submenu where you can configure the settings
for each of the &krayon; tools.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice></term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the main menu, or hides it. The menubar is at the top
of the &krayon; window.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the main toolbar, or hides it.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the statusbar, or hides it. The statusbar is at the
bottom of the &krayon; window.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Sidebar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the sidebar, or hides it. The sidebar is at the left
of the &krayon; window. It contains color, brush, pattern and
other controls.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Krayon Preferences...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Opens the Preferences dialog. You use this dialog to set
your user and work settings for &krayon;.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Save Options</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Save the current settings and options for &krayon;. This
will save all settings made in the Settings menu and its dialogs.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show File Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the file toolbar or hides it. This toolbar contains
icons to create, open, save or print the current image.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Selection Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the selection toolbar, or hides it. This toolbar
contains icons to copy, cut, remove or paste the image selection.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show KrayonBox Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the KrayonBox toolbar, or hides it. This toolbar
contains icons to open the colors, krayons, brushes, patterns,
layers and channels dialogs.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Settings Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the Settings toolbar, or hides it. This toolbar
contains icons to show or hide the sidebar, or open various
settings dialogs.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Show Tools Toolbar</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Shows the Tools toolbar, or hides it. This toolbar contains
icons for the drawing tools. </para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Configure key bindings...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Opens the <guilabel>Configure Key Bindings</guilabel>
dialog. This dialog is used to change what keystrokes are
associated with an action.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Opens the <guilabel>Configure Toolbars</guilabel>
dialog. This dialog is used to customize the toolbar layouts and
actions.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="help-menu">
<title>The <guimenu>Help</guimenu> Menu</title>

<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycap>F1</keycap></shortcut>
<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Contents</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Opens up the &krayon; Handbook in the &kde; Help Center.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">
&Ctrl;<keycap>F1</keycap>
</keycombo></shortcut>
<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Changes the cursor to a <guilabel>What's This?</guilabel>
cursor. When this cursor is clicked on an item, icon or other
control, a quick help panel is displayed.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Opens up the <guilabel>Submit a Bug Report</guilabel>
dialog. If you find a defect in &krayon; use this dialog to report
it to the &krayon; developers.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>About Krayon...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Displays copyright and other information for &krayon;.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>
<menuchoice>
<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>About KDE...</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>
</term>
<listitem>
<para>Displays copyright and other information for the K Desktop
Environment.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>

</sect1>

